Liverpool and Manchester United are reportedly set to lose out to Bayern Munich in the race for highly-rated Lille winger Pepe. The Ivory Coast star has attracted the attention of elite European clubs this season following an impressive campaign in Ligue 1. Both Liverpool and United have been linked with the 24-year-old for several months, but are now poised to look out after Bayern upped the intensity of their approach in order to seal a deal....read 
